metadata.description:
🐉DIVINE BEAST & ANIMALS🐶_GUNZO-ZU_YUKI KOYANO👨‍👩‍👧‍👧
NFT of 'DIVINE BEAST & ANIMALS' consisting of 888 collections by Yuki Koyano.
It consists of close-ups of 8 kinds of divine beasts and 8 kinds of animals in my paintings.
Encountering unique 'DIVINE BEAST & ANIMALS' that have never been seen before is the key to better understanding Yuki Koyano's art and 'GUNZO-ZU' paintings.
From the new 888 NFTs to the display, you can enjoy digital to analog from various angles, such as experiencing, owning, creating communities, and participating in exhibitions. Let's start the future that goes back and forth between Metaverse x Art x Exhibition from these.
